high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the small black table next to the couch.
Pick up the set of keys off of the small black table.
Turn around and walk over to the door, then turn left and walk over to the glass table.
Put the set of keys in the cardboard box on the table.
Pick up the cardboard box with the keys in it off of the table.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a right and walk around the glass table to the back of the red chair.
Put the cardboard box with the keys in it on the seat of the red chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with keys in it on a red chair.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the keys on the small table.
Pick up the keys on the small table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the dining room table.
Place the keys in the box on the table.
Pick up the box on the table.
Turn left and walk forward to face the back of the red arm chair.
Place the box on the red arm chair.
anns.task_desc: To put a set of keys in a box as well as move them to the red arm chair.

high_descs: Turn right and move forward slightly then turn right and walk straight to the lamp
Pick up the keys from the table next to the lamp and sofa
Turn around and walk straight to the door then turn left and walk to the kitchen table with a box on it and face it
Place the keys in the box on the table
Pick up the box with the keys inside
Turn left walk straight slightly then turn right and walk to the red sofa chair and face it
Place the box on the seat cushion of the red chair
anns.task_desc: Move keys to a box on the chair
